<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Post Created</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg: #f3f3f1;
            --paper: #ffffff;
            --ink: #111111;
            --muted: #5f5f5f;
            --soft-line: rgba(17, 17, 17, 0.08);
            --shadow: 16px 16px 0 #111111;
            font-family: "SF Pro Display", "SF Pro Text", -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
        }

        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        html,
        body {
            margin: 0;
            min-height: 100%;
        }

        body {
            display: grid;
            place-items: center;
            padding: 24px;
            color: var(--ink);
            background:
                linear-gradient(to right, var(--soft-line) 1px, transparent 1px),
                linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--soft-line) 1px, transparent 1px),
                var(--bg);
            background-size: 32px 32px, 32px 32px, auto;
        }

        .overlay {
            width: min(560px, 100%);
            padding: 28px;
            border: 2px solid var(--ink);
            background: var(--paper);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
        }

        .eyebrow,
        .button {
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.16em;
        }

        .eyebrow {
            margin: 0 0 18px;
            font-size: 0.76rem;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        h1 {
            margin: 0;
            max-width: 10ch;
            font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 8vw, 4.8rem);
            line-height: 0.94;
            letter-spacing: -0.06em;
        }

        p {
            max-width: 34rem;
            margin: 20px 0 0;
            color: var(--muted);
            font-size: 1rem;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }

        .button-row {
            margin-top: 28px;
            padding-top: 22px;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--ink);
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            min-height: 46px;
            padding: 0 18px;
            border: 1.5px solid var(--ink);
            background: var(--ink);
            color: var(--paper);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 0.78rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            transition: background-color 140ms ease, color 140ms ease;
        }

        .button:hover,
        .button:focus-visible {
            background: var(--paper);
            color: var(--ink);
            outline: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <main class="overlay">
        <p class="eyebrow">Success</p>
        <h1>Post created.</h1>
        <p>
            The article has been saved successfully. You can return to the editor
            and create another post right away.
        </p>

        <div class="button-row">
            <a class="button" href="/integrations/cardform">Back to Editor</a>
        </div>
    </main>
</body>
</html>
